Content: This is a known issue with Tor. It doesn't encrypt data, it just anonymizes it. If you put unencrypted info in Tor, it comes out on the other side unencrypted.

Author: gtmcknight
Content:
An oldie but goodie TED Talk. These are consistently the most engaging and interesting speeches. FYI I run a video site called Chime.TV and we created a channel just for TED Talks: http://chime.tv/tedtalks

Recent ones I've enjoyed are Erin McKean's Redifining The Dictionary ( http://chime.tv/tedtalks/3l9sg ) and Rives: Is 4AM The New Midnight? ( http://chime.tv/tedtalks/2gdlw )
